HEADWORD: Truckage
<hw>Truck"age</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The practice of
bartering goods; exchange; barter; truck.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>truckage</qex> of perishing coin.</q>
