==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Truckage
<hw>Truck"age</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Money paid for the conveyance of
goods on a truck; freight.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trucker</ent>⟦br⟧
